[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……と、いうわけで。\n恥ずかしながら帰ってまいりました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01333",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "わーい！　やったーーーっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01334",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ぬぬぬ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01335",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ヨハナ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01336",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "私の涙、返しなさいよーーーーっ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01337",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "うう……お騒がせしてすまない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01338",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ともあれ、これで元通りですわね。\n幸い、まだ外部には情報を出していませんし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01339",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "社長殿。またお世話になりまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01340",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ。今年はさらに忙しくなりますわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01341",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "精一杯頑張らせていただきまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01342",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "家のことが忙しいからってサボらないでよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01343",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "当然！　両立すると決めたのだからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01344",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そういえば。来週にはこの学園も新学期がスタート。\nこの教室が使えるのもあと数日ですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01345",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "え！　じゃあ練習場所はどうすれば……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01346",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ。ご安心なさいな。近日、\nララ・プロダクションの新スタジオが完成しますわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01347",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "なんと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01348",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "今後は我が社もアイドル路線に力を入れていくつもり\nですので、そのための投資ですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01349",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "アタシたち、先輩になるかもしれないんだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01350",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "どんな後輩が入ってくるか楽しみね。\n……ま、私レベルの奴はそうそういないでしょうけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01351",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者たちも負けていられませんな！\n早速レッスンといこう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01352",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "おーー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01353",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（夢）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01354",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（夢）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01355",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（夢）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01356",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（みんなの夢はなに？）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01357",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（光なんて１つもないステージでも）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01358",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちは夢を見る）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01359",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（さあ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01360",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（さあ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01361",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（さあ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01362",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちの――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01363",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちの――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01364",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちの――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01365",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ＬＩＦＥが始まる！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01366",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ＬＩＦＥが始まる！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01367",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ＬＩＦＥが始まる！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01368",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
